-- Events / Communication
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

---Triggers an event programmatically.
---@param element integer Element index
---@param event integer Event type
function event_trigger(element, event) end

---Sends a string via WebSocket.
---@param message string
function websocket_send(message) end

---Sends a package to the editor.
